org.vngx.jsch.algorithm

Class CompressionImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vngx.jsch.algorithm.CompressionImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Algorithm, Compression

    public final class CompressionImpl
extends Object
implements Compression

    Implementation of Compression which uses the JCraft jzlib library to compress and/or uncompress byte data.

    Note: This class is not thread-safe and must be externally synchronized.

    Author:
    Atsuhiko Yamanaka, Michael Laudati
    See Also:
    JZlib, ZStream, org.vngx.jsch.Compression
